### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### List All Stations
GET http://localhost:3000/stations

###

### Get Specific Station
GET http://localhost:3000/stations/44009

###

### Get Observations for Station
# With default limit
GET http://localhost:3000/observations/by-station/44009

###

### Get Observations with Limit
GET http://localhost:3000/observations/by-station/44009?limit=50

###

### Get Observations Since Date
GET http://localhost:3000/observations/by-station/44009?since=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z

###

### Get Observations with Limit and Since
GET http://localhost:3000/observations/by-station/44009?limit=20&since=2024-01-15T00:00:00Z

###

### Real-Time Stream (SSE)
# Note: This will keep the connection open
# Press Ctrl+C to disconnect
GET http://localhost:3000/stream

###

### Test Invalid Station ID
GET http://localhost:3000/stations/invalid-id

###

### Test Missing Station
GET http://localhost:3000/stations/99999

